    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS timing. This specimen boasts a flawless Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a reinforced subframe and original bushings showing zero degradation. Every mechanical component, from the high-revving valvetrain to the precision-tuned suspension, operates in perfect harmony. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
